Mike Williams (boxer) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mike_Williams_(boxer) 0 Michael Anthony Williams (born June 16, 1962) is an American actor and former professional boxer who competed from 1984 to 2000. He is most notable for portraying fictional boxer Union Cane in the 1990 film Rocky V.
